<h2 >幸福相处五大绝招让爱情经久不衰</h2>
<div class="text clear" id="contentText">
				<div style="background: none transparent scroll repeat 0% 0%; border: #d4d4d4 1px solid; padding: 10px;" class="abstract bgB clear">　　 什麽是高品质的家庭和感情？80後的夫妻应该怎麽去相处？</div>
<div class="text-pic">
<table class="tableImg" border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" align="center">
